<div class="container">
			<div class="section-box">
				<div class="navbar">
					<h2 class="welcome-banner">
					 Hi and Welcome to the 100 Motels Demo<br>
					 <small>100 Motels is an idea I have to help independent musicians like myself get out on tour without industry backing or paying to play.</small>
					</h2>
	  			<div id="welcome-nav" class="navbar-inner" align="center">
	  				<div class="label-box"><del>Alpha</del> Demo!!</div>
	  				<a class="brand">Click One >></a>
						<ul class="nav">
							<li class="divider-vertical"></li>
							<li class="span2"><a href="#new-promoters">Tour or Support</a></li>
		  				<li class="span2"><a href="#promoter-apply">Organize</a></li>
		  				<li class="span2"><a href="#latest-events">Tickets</a></li>
		  				<li class="span3"><%= link_to "What is 100 Motels? ", info_path %></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		<div id="content">

			<section id="latest-events">
				<header class="page-header">
					<h3>
						<i class="icon-globe"></i>
						Shows near <%= @location %> <%= link_to "View All >>", events_path, class: "pull-right btn" %>
					</h3>
				</header>
				<div id="events-carousel" class="carousel slide" data-interval="false">
					<div class="carousel-inner">
						<% @locations.each_slice(3) do |loc| %>
						<div class="item">
								<ul class="thumbnails">
									<li class="span4">
										<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if loc[0].event.image? %>
												<%= filepicker_image_tag loc[0].event.image, w: 360, h: 240, fit: 'crop' %>
											<% else %>
												<img src="http://quickimage.it/360x240&text=ArtistPic" alt="">
											<% end %>
											<div class="caption">
												<h4 class="title">
													<%= loc[0].event.artist %>
												</h4>
												<p><%= loc[0].event.venue %> on <%= time_tag loc[0].event.date %></p>
												<%= button_to "Info & Tickets", event_path(loc[0].event), method: :get, class: "btn btn-success", id: loc[0].event.artist %>
											</div>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li class="span4">
										<% if loc[1] %>
											<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if loc[1].event.image? %>
												<%= filepicker_image_tag loc[1].event.image, w: 360, h: 240, fit: 'crop' %>
											<% else %>
												<img src="http://quickimage.it/360x240&text=ArtistPic" alt="">
											<% end %>
											<div class="caption">
												<h4 class="title">
													<%= loc[1].event.artist %>
												</h4>
												<p><%= loc[1].event.venue %> on <%= time_tag loc[1].event.date %></p>
												<%= button_to "Info & Tickets", event_path(loc[1].event), method: :get, class: "btn btn-success", id: loc[1].event.artist %>
											</div>
											</div>
										<% else %>

										<% end %>
									</li>
									<li class="span4">
										<% if loc[2] %>
											<div class="thumbnail">
												<% if loc[2].event.image? %>
													<%= filepicker_image_tag loc[2].event.image, w: 360, h: 240, fit: 'crop' %>
												<% else %>
													<img src="http://quickimage.it/360x240&text=ArtistPic" alt="">
												<% end %>
												<div class="caption">
													<h4 class="title">
														<%= loc[2].event.artist %>
													</h4>
													<p><%= loc[2].event.venue %> on <%= time_tag loc[2].event.date %></p>
													<%= button_to "Info & Tickets", event_path(loc[2].event), method: :get, class: "btn btn-success", id: loc[2].event.artist %>
												</div>
											</div>
										<% else %>

										<% end %>
									</li>
								</ul>
						</div>
						<% end %>
					</div>
					<a class="left carousel-control" href="#events-carousel" data-slide="prev">‹</a>
					<a class="right carousel-control" href="#events-carousel" data-slide="next">›</a>
				</div>
				<hr>
			</section>

			<section id="new-promoters">
				<header>
					<h3 class="page-header"><i class="icon-globe"></i>Organizers near <%= @location %> <%= link_to "View All >>", promoter_profiles_path, class: "pull-right btn" %></h3>
				</header>
				<div id="promoters-carousel" class="carousel slide" data-interval="false">
					<div id="promoters" class="carousel-inner">
						<% @profiles.each_slice(4) do |profile| %>
						<div class="item">
								<ul class="thumbnails">
									<li class="span3">
										<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if profile[0] %>
												<% if profile[0].image? %>
				                  <%= filepicker_image_tag profile[0].image, w: 360, h: 360, fit: 'crop' %>
				                <% else %>
				                  <img src="http://placehold.it/360x360" alt="">
				                <% end %>
													<div class="caption">
														<h3 class="title"><%= profile[0].promoter_name || profile[0].user.name %></h3>
														<h4>location</h4>
														<%= button_to "Full Profile", profile_path(profile[0]), method: :get, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
												</div>
											<% end %>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li class="span3">
										<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if profile[1] %>
												<% if profile[1].image? %>
				                  <%= filepicker_image_tag profile[1].image, w: 360, h: 360, fit: 'crop' %>
				                <% else %>
				                  <img src="http://placehold.it/360x360" alt="">
				                <% end %>
												<div class="caption">
													<h3 class="title"><%= profile[1].promoter_name || profile[1].user.name %></h3>
													<h4>location</h4>
													<%= button_to "Full Profile", profile_path(profile[1]), method: :get, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
												</div>
											<% end %>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li class="span3">
										<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if profile[2] %>
												<% if profile[2].image? %>
				                  <%= filepicker_image_tag profile[2].image, w: 360, h: 360, fit: 'crop' %>
				                <% else %>
				                  <img src="http://placehold.it/360x360" alt="">
				                <% end %>
												<div class="caption">
													<h3 class="title"><%= profile[2].promoter_name || profile[2].user.name %></h3>
													<h4>location</h4>
													<%= button_to "Full Profile", profile_path(profile[2]), method: :get, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
												</div>
											<% end %>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li class="span3">
										<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if profile[3] %>
												<% if profile[3].image? %>
				                  <%= filepicker_image_tag profile[3].image, w: 360, h: 360, fit: 'crop' %>
				                <% else %>
				                  <img src="http://placehold.it/360x360" alt="">
				                <% end %>
												<div class="caption">
													<h3 class="title"><%= profile[3].promoter_name || profile[3].user.name %></h3>
													<h4>location</h4>
													<%= button_to "Full Profile", profile_path(profile[3]), method: :get, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
												</div>
											<% end %>
										</div>
									</li>
								</ul>
						</div>
						<% end %>
					</div>
					<a class="left carousel-control" href="#promoters-carousel" data-slide="prev">‹</a>
					<a class="right carousel-control" href="#promoters-carousel" data-slide="next">›</a>
				</div>
				<hr>
			</section>

			<section id="promoter-apply">
				<div class="well well-large">
					<header><h3 class="lead">So Who Organizes the Show?</h3></header>
					<div class="row-fluid">
						<div class="span2">
							<p>
								<img src="//www.gravatar.com/avatar/fd4e9587dd4e9696fecfa8b47f5d6c77.png" class="img-circle">
							</p>
							<ul class="nav nav-list">
			          <li class="nav-header">How it Works</li>
			          <li class="divider"></li>
			          <li><%= link_to "Organizing", info_path(anchor: "organizing") %></li>
			          <li><%= link_to "Funding", info_path(anchor: "funding") %></li>
			          <li><%= link_to "Touring", info_path(anchor: "touring") %></li>
			          <li><%= link_to "Supporting", info_path(anchor: "supporting") %></li>
			          <li><%= link_to "Attending", info_path(anchor: "attending") %></li>
			          <br>
			          <li class="divider"></li>
			        </ul>
			        <div class="btn-group center">
								<a href="#invite" class="btn btn-block btn-large btn-primary" data-toggle="modal">Request Invite</a>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="span10">
							<blockquote>
								<p><strong>Anyone...excepting Artists.</strong> </p>
								<br>
								<p>Artists can do three things on 100 Motels: Add a playlist of their music; make a tour request; make a support request. If they end up playing a show, everything bar the performance will be taken care of by the organizer. It's just like the pro's, except you don't have to make commercial music to play.<strong> You will never pay to play.</strong></p> <br>
							  <p>Anyone who has a credit card can organize, but it will be controlled until the service matures. The first organizers will be radio hosts, bloggers and other proven contributers to music without profit who naturally command a crowd. Check out the organizers in this demo, all people who I discovered through my music.</p> <br>
								<p>Along with offloading the organizational burden from the artist there were two other pillar issues that precipitated the idea for 100 Motels: Risk and Attendance. You can organize or fund a 100 Motels show without incurring any costs. A successful campaign is always realised in terms of attaining a target attendance. </p> <br>
								<p>Follow the adjacent links for more info or for the full details of the implementation <%= link_to "go here.", info_path %></p>
							</blockquote>
						</div>
						<hr>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
		<div class="modal hide fade" id="invite" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">x</button>
        <h3>100 Motels Promoter Invites</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Thanks for your interest. Right now I'm testing amongst people I know, so if you've stumbled onto this site somehow this is really only a demo, 100 Motels is not open for business yet. If you want to contact me about getting involved message me on twitter, facebook, github or whatever you use, <a href="//seocahill.com">Seo.</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <a href="#" class="btn" data-dismiss="modal">Close</a>
      </div>
    </div>
 </div>




